{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "20.1",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2890e5b",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "それでは……解散して各々自由に過ごすといたしましょうか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.1",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d617c3a3",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "えっ、か、解散？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.1",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "90fa0ccf",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "雫……２人に宇宙船を案内しなきゃ駄目、でしょ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.1",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f475295e",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……そうでございました。船内を案内いたしますね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e540ad93",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（今確実に俺たちのことを放置するつもりだったな……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.1",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "12254122",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あっ！　じゃあさ、じゃあさ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.1",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "febf39a2",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょっと外に出てみてもいい？　風とかすごいんじゃないかな！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2296213",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お、確かに！　すげえスピード出てるんだよな？　ちょっと顔出すくらいならいけるんじゃないか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.1",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b4ceccba",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "えっ……と……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.1",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4e2f6eaa",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……案内の前に、お２人には宇宙について説明したほうがよろしいですね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.1",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5afa9148",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "宇宙ってね……そのまま外に出たら、死んじゃう……の……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.1",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "33dfab79",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ええっ！？　そうなの！？　なんで！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.1",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "31b740d1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "わかりやすくお伝えするならば……空気はありませんし、凄く寒いうえ、危険な見えない物も飛び交っています",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.1",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "857c7599",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "外に出る方法はありますが、対策しなければとにかく死にます",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d463d682",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "か……顔だけでも？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.1",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2d95f284",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……マグマに一瞬浸かっても大丈夫なら大丈夫ではないでしょうか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.0",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bc72796b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ひぇー……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "66.1",
      "line_index": 66,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8ce5db9b",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "だから、この船の窓は開かないし……それと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "76.1",
      "line_index": 76,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "dd68c32f",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "っ…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1f7610d9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "話していたルミナがよろめく。近くの椅子に座り込む前に、雫が素早く抱きとめた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.1",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7e7e1718",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ルミナ様！　いけません！　すぐにお部屋で休みませんと！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.1",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a8db6e05",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "そう……だね。色々無理……しすぎたみたい……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "88.0",
      "line_index": 88,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "af371893",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "だ、大丈夫か……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6f94767d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "気遣うと、ルミナがこちらに力ない笑みを返す。そして１人で扉のほうへと歩き出すが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.1",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c3bd77e",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "いけませんルミナ様、私がお送りを……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.1",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f97ce548",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "大丈夫、一人で行けるから……二人に、続きを案内して？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.1",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "eca5b925",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ですが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.1",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a7a9714f",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "大丈夫、何かあったらアポロもいるから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.1",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6aaf5a99",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……かしこまりました。お気をつけて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.1",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b6f187ba",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "…………？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.0",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "99bac503",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（アポロ……？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "75744a1a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "雫は深々と頭を下げ、ルミナは部屋を出ていった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "123.1",
      "line_index": 123,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "99ac86cb",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "さて、では説明の続きをいたしましょう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "125.0",
      "line_index": 125,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ddc40e2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "大丈夫なのか？　従者なのに、ルミナから離れて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.1",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2b0fbb77",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ルミナ様も、お１人になりたい時間はあります",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.1",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "62c29e35",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "風邪とかひいてないといいけど……あとでポーション持っていこうか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.1",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8f80cabf",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "いいえ。リリアンなので問題は無いとは思いますが、別の星の薬を軽々に飲用することは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.1",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "98de95dc",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そっか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.1",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "915ea1cf",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "141.1",
      "line_index": 141,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "22ac1620",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "気を取り直しまして。宇宙という物の基本の説明を続けましょう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.1",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b84495a3",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あ、そうだそうだ。宇宙ってつまり、何もない空間が広がってるんだよね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.1",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fca4361e",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "おおよそ間違いございません",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.1",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "55f096da",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "じゃあ何で星とか、色々浮いてるの？　魔力？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.1",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6e0b30fc",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……重力と呼ばれる物が、世界にはありまして",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.0",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3a6901f3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "重力……物が落ちる力だよな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "153.1",
      "line_index": 153,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "760c69a2",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ああ良かった……そこはご存知でしたか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.1",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "40cf4b8b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "地の神に愛される物は重くて、天の神に愛される物は軽いんだよね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.1",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e4cdc1df",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.1",
      "line_index": 167,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d687e307",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "え、ここからでございますか？　いえ、むしろどこからでございますか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "169.1",
      "line_index": 169,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "aee6e93d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ど、どうしたの……？　何か悪いこと言っちゃった？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "179.0",
      "line_index": 179,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "61ead7ac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "十数分後…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.1",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cf8474ef",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "へえ、つまり色んな星に地の神様がいて、神様の力が届かないところは浮いちゃうんだ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.0",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "171a41b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "大きい星ほどその引っ張る力が強いってことでいいのか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.1",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6759fb09",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ええ……まあ……そのような感じで",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.0",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "98120bc3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（なんかどうも本当は違うけど一旦コレにしとこう感あるな……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.1",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d03b159a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "それでその重力……が無いところを動ける乗り物が、宇宙船でございます",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "199.1",
      "line_index": 199,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "69bb53aa",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "なるほどぉ……あたし達が住んでたみたいなところもいっぱいあるのかな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "201.1",
      "line_index": 201,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ea4691b",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ございますが……数は多くありません。殆どは生命がいない星でございます",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "203.1",
      "line_index": 203,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "96212643",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そうなんだ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "205.0",
      "line_index": 205,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2c327862",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あっ！　でもそれって、食料とかは……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "207.1",
      "line_index": 207,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f2b6a606",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あ、そうか！　何もない空間で生き物もいない星が多いなら、ご飯とかお水とか大変なんじゃ……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.1",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "69747978",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "蓄えや生産設備は整っておりますのでご心配なく。……時々星に降りて物資を調達する必要はございますが",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "211.1",
      "line_index": 211,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "82c673f5",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "せいさんせつび……って？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "213.1",
      "line_index": 213,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "39a6917",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "植物を自動的に育成・収穫する設備や、菌類を培養して食用肉を作り出す設備もございます",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "219.1",
      "line_index": 219,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "12e5df4d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……よくわかんないけど、すごーい！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "221.1",
      "line_index": 221,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a8647041",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……これは、案内をする場所や情報をかなり絞り込んだほうがよさそうですね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.0",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e580b54c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "い、いや……高い技術が使われてるのはわかるから、ある程度はお願いしたいんだが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "225.1",
      "line_index": 225,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3d06ea7c",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "はあ……では廊下に出て別の部屋を案内いたしますが、休んでいるルミナ様の邪魔をしないようにお願いいたします。くれぐれも",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "227.1",
      "line_index": 227,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1e1daa2f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "はーい！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "229.0",
      "line_index": 229,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6e678e4b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（ルミナ……大丈夫かな？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "243.1",
      "line_index": 243,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "136e66",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "……ふう……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "245.1",
      "line_index": 245,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8dec9af9",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "261.1",
      "line_index": 261,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a45d3685",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "私、あなたと前にも……それで、あの……婚約……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "263.0",
      "line_index": 263,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "370037de",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "え…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "265.0",
      "line_index": 265,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5e4a2a0c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "………………ごめん。覚えて、ないな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "267.1",
      "line_index": 267,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b6c7d7a",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "そう……なん、だ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "269.0",
      "line_index": 269,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8b97fa70",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "人違いとかじゃ、ないよな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "271.1",
      "line_index": 271,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d86c9963",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "……うん……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "284.1",
      "line_index": 284,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8dec9af9",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "286.1",
      "line_index": 286,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7110ef7e",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "私……馬鹿、みたい……",
      "zh": ""
